definitions.definition: The sweet, usually red , edible accessory fruit of certain plants of the genus Fragaria .
examples: They went to pick strawberries today.

definitions.definition: Any plant of the genus Fragaria (that bears such fruit).
examples: She has the best strawberry patch I've ever seen.

definitions.definition: The berry of the strawberry tree ( Arbutus )
A dark pinkish red color , like that of the fruit; strawberry red .
Something resembling a strawberry, especially a reddish bruise, birthmark , or infantile hemangioma ( naevus ).
A prostitute who exchanges sexual services for crack cocaine .
